snippet.title: Unreleased Metallica video game Trailer **Original Quality**
snippet.description:
**Best viewed when you add &fmt=18 to the end of the URL**

This is the trailer for the unrealeased untitled Metallica video game. The trailer can be found when you insert the St. Anger CD into your computer.

This video is the original quality and untampered with. Pulled directly from the St. Anger CD.


GET HYPED FOR GUITAR HERO: METALLICA! \m/ METALLICA ROOOOOCKS!
